### Test Case 1.4: Report Status for Non-Existent Agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/report_status
Content-Type: application/json
#Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "agentId": "agent-non-existent",
  "running": true,
  "pendingTasks": 1,
  "runningTasks": 0,
  "finishedTasks": 0,
